1
00:00:03,000 --> 00:00:06,500
Today's class is calligraphy. Please be quiet.

2
00:00:08,000 --> 00:00:11,200
Nishikata, are you good at calligraphy?

3
00:00:12,500 --> 00:00:15,800
I'm average, I guess. What about you, Takagi-san?

4
00:00:17,000 --> 00:00:20,500
Me? Hmm, I'm okay, I suppose.

5
00:00:22,000 --> 00:00:25,300
Then, want to have a contest? To see who writes better.

6
00:00:27,000 --> 00:00:30,000
Sure. What does the loser have to do?

7
00:00:31,500 --> 00:00:34,800
The loser has to... do one thing the winner says!

8
00:00:36,000 --> 00:00:39,500
Sounds fun. Okay, let's do it.

9
00:00:41,000 --> 00:00:44,200
All right, I'm definitely going to win!

10
00:00:46,000 --> 00:00:49,500
The subject will be "Friend." Please look at my example.

11
00:00:51,000 --> 00:00:54,300
I don't have enough ink. I'll put on a bit more.

12
00:00:56,000 --> 00:00:59,000
Nishikata, you're holding the brush a little wrong.

13
00:01:00,500 --> 00:01:03,800
Huh, really? What's wrong with it?

14
00:01:05,000 --> 00:01:08,500
You should hold it a bit higher. Like this.

15
00:01:10,000 --> 00:01:13,200
Oh, you're right. Thanks.

16
00:01:15,000 --> 00:01:18,500
Done! How is it? I think I wrote it pretty well.

17
00:01:20,000 --> 00:01:23,300
Yeah, it's good. But mine might be better.

18
00:01:25,000 --> 00:01:28,000
Whoa... it really is good.

19
00:01:29,500 --> 00:01:33,000
So, I win then. You'll do one thing I ask, okay?

20
00:01:34,500 --> 00:01:38,000
What are you planning to ask... That's scary.
